  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate safety and efficacy in the actual use of REVOLADE collected from all subjects
      receiving the drug until data from a specified number of subjects are accumulated to identify
      factors considered to influence its safety and efficacy.

      &lt;Priority investigation item&gt; Thromboembolism
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
